metadata.name: StarryNight - Priority Pass #1
metadata.description: The StarryNight - Priority Pass is a 1K NFT collection that comes in the form of a certificate granted to Priority List VIPs and can be used to redeem the NFT StarryNight collection, the first 10K NFT project developed by ArteX inspired by the world's most renowned artists and the most famous paintings in history. Each Priority Pass StarryNight can be exchanged for one NFT StarryNight at the public sale.
